import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.exp(x0)
    v1 = jnp.exp(v0)
    v2 = jnp.tanh(x0)
    v3 = jnp.maximum(x1, v2)
    v4 = jnp.exp(v0)
    v5 = jnp.exp(v3)
    v6 = jnp.multiply(v4, v5)
    v7 = jnp.abs(v5)
    v8 = jnp.maximum(v5, v7)
    v9 = jnp.abs(v8)
